entries.femaleVariant: If you're looking for a guide, Trevor's the one.
Did you hear those bastards killed Trevor?
What do you mean? He's a good kid. Quick, clever...
OK, let me be more precise – I need a guide who is not Trevor.
I know a few Trevors. Every last one of them has shit for brains.
Wait, wait, wait – h-how'd they get him? During a job, a raid?
Why does that not surprise me?
Hey, come on. He was a good kid. And he deserves some payback...
To the Wraiths? On business? That boy was askin' for trouble.
Well, no... Trevor went to them himself. On business.
